 words in a statement is at least twice the loessed proportion of negative
 words, and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

low
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 otherwise.
 I constructed another categorical variable representing the four possible
 states in this model: 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

FARC/low,
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

FARC/high,
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

government/low,
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

government/high.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
