 Even when the seed is set to a fixed integer in R, the EM algorithm does
 not always produce the same results, meaning that it does not reliably
 generate the same transition matrix.
 It does, however, reliably generate a limited number of transition matrices:
 three different matrices for FARC, and four for the government.
 I fitted the model 1,000 times for each of FARC and the government and
 used the most frequently occurring model (596/1000 for FARC, 916/1000 for
